title: League of Legends Stats Analysis
description: Designed and conducted a hypothesis test on the collected data of the 2022 League of Legends World Championship event. Analyzed statistical patterns and trends to validate or refute the proposed hypothesis. Presented findings through a formatted report published on a website.

title: Big Data GUI
description: Developed a GUI that sorts and displays the different crime reports by selected category. Utilized the police department incident report data spanning from January 2003 to May 2018.

title: Bikewatching Geospatial Visualization
description: A geospatial visualization showing bike datas located in Boston and Cambridge. The green lines are the bike lanes, circles are the Blue Bike stations and the colors represent the traffic at the destinations. There's also a filter for the traffic at specific time of the day.

title: Text Excel
description: Developed a replica of the functionality and capabilities of a spreadsheet. Programmed core operations such as data input, editing, cell references, and formula calculations
